com.trendrr.json.simple.parser
Interface ContentHandler

public interface ContentHandler

A simplified and stoppable SAX-like content handler for stream processing of JSON text.

Author:
FangYidong
See Also:
org.xml.sax.ContentHandler, org.json.simple.parser.JSONParser#parse(java.io.Reader, ContentHandler, boolean)
